   <topic><![CDATA[FILE.DIR_GET Function]]></topic>
   <syntax>Current_Directory as C = Dir_Get()</syntax>
   <description>Get the current working directory.</description>
   <arguments>
   <argument>
  
   <name>Current_Directory</name>
   <description>The path and name of the current directory.</description>
   </argument>
   </arguments>
   
   
   <discussion><![CDATA[
The FILE.DIR_GET() method returns the name of the current directory.]]>
   </discussion>
   
   <example><![CDATA[
? file.dir_get()
= "C:\Spread" 
]]></example>
   
